data.description: THIS COULD BE THE ONE!! This stunning condo offers an exceptional long lake view, which is a rare find in the Casa Di Fiori community. Only a few units on the second floor have this breathtaking view, making it a truly exceptional opportunity. The unit has only had one owner and was built in 2016 but has been lived in for less than three years, from 2021 to the present.    Inside, you'll find beautiful ceramic tile floors laid on the diagonal, granite countertops, and Sienna Rope kitchen cabinets with a large matching pantry. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, and the sale also includes the washer and dryer. Moreover, the living room/dining area has cathedral ceilings, making it feel open and airy.    This unique building has only four units downstairs and four units upstairs! Don't miss out on the chance to see this exceptional condo for yourself!
